data.description: This updated NW side Ranch is just waiting for its new owners to make it their own! This home has tons of updates from top to bottom in just the past few years. Walk in and find your open living room in the front which leads to your kitchen which has been updated over the years with stainless steel appliances. Around the corner you will find a dining area with a walkout to your screened in back porch which was renovated in 2015. Upstairs you will find 3 freshly painted bedrooms and 1 full bathroom. The wide open basement just puts the cherry on the top with luxury vinyl plank flooring and a bar which is perfect for entertaining. The large fenced backyard is great for playing around or just relaxing around the fire pit. The 2 car attached garage is another huge plus for those cold Iowa winters. Some major replacements are the Roof in 2021, windows in 2013, A/C and Furnace in 2017 and the water heater is only 8 years old!
